room_title: Escape room "The Christmas Crisis" by The Art of Escape: ICT in Wichita
room_description:
It is the most wonderful time of the year! Christmas Eve has come, but something is amiss. Santa's magic comes from a very special Holiday tradition - warm cookies, and Mrs. Claus' is feeling a bit under the weather this year, and won't be able to make them!
â€‹The time has come for you and your team to enter Mrs. Claus' bakery workshop and find her special recipe book, get the ingredients, and get the cookies made before midnight - you have one hour to save Christmas for the entire world, so let the Christmas Crisis begin!
